# -*- mode: conf -*-
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User rynffoll@gmail.com
PassCmd "LANG=C gpg -q -d ~/.authinfo.gpg | awk '/imap\.gmail/ { print $8 }'"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Maildir/
Inbox ~/Maildir/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "![Gmail]*" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash" "!ML*" "ML/*"
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
Create Slave
SyncState *
